reviewText: HAD TO HAVE A COPY TO KEEP ME INTERESTED UNTIL I LEAVE FOR AMSTERDAM.
Thought this would give some funny insight into the Amsterdam scene... it was just a poorly shot diatribe about getting high in Amsterdam.  It was a terrible documentary about said activity.

I received this dvd from netflix one day, expecting it to be just another 'stoner' documentary. Relief washed over me shortly into the dvd. While this is definitely not a big budget film, it makes up for it in heart and soul. I love it's simplistic look at the coffee shops of Amsterdam.
